    "content": "Hi Ms. Patricia,\n\n‌\n\n It was a pleasure connecting with you earlier—thanks again for taking the time. I understand you already have someone assisting with the RMA process for your SolarEdge inverter replacement, which means you’re already moving in the right direction.\n\n‌\n\n If that process isn’t moving as quickly as you’d like, or if the company isn’t equipped to handle the full replacement, our local crew is ready to step in right away. Our **quote is $680 for the complete inverter replacement**, including a 24-month warranty. _We’ll resolve the core issue so you won’t have to face the same problem again._\n\n‌\n\n Since your system was originally managed by Titan Solar, which is no longer operating, _you now have the opportunity to benefit from our remote monitoring and proactive support._ Once your site is running again, we’ll not only monitor it for errors but also _troubleshoot any installation-related issues remotely—before they affect performance._ This service is a **one-time $120 investment in ongoing system health.**\n\n‌\n\n To make things easy, just snap a quick photo or jot down:\n\n- **Inverter Serial Number:** Found on the silver label on the right side of your inverter.\n  ‌\n- **Site ID:** In your MySolarEdge app, tap the menu (top left), then “Site Details.”\n  ‌\n\n When you’re ready, _send those over and we’ll take it from there—your solar peace of mind is just a message away._\n\n‌\n\n Looking forward to helping you maximize your system monthy savings. \n\n‌\n\n Best,\n\n Cesar Jurado\n\n Conexsol\n\n (213)278-4926",
